quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  28,12,WE HERREMNA ‘ALEJHIL-MERADI’A MIN KABLU FEKALET HEL ‘EDULLUKUM ‘ALA ‘EHLI BEJTIN JEKFULUNEHU LEKUM WE HUM LEHU NASIHUNE
  28,13,FEREDEDNAHU ‘ILA ‘UMMIHI KEJ TEKARRE ‘AJNUHA WE LA TEHZENE WE LITA’LEME ‘ENNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  28,14,WE LEMMA BELEGA ‘ESHUDDEHU WE ESTEWA ‘ATEJNAHU HUKMÆN WE ‘ILMÆN WE KEDHELIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  28,15,WE DEHALEL-MEDINETE ‘ALA HINI GAFLETIN MIN ‘EHLIHA FEWEXHEDE FIHA REXHULEJNI JEKTETILANI HADHA MIN SHI’ATIHI WE HEDHA MIN ‘ADUWIHI FASTEGATHEHUL-LEDHI MIN SHI’ATIHI ‘ALEL-LEDHI MIN ‘ADUWIHI FEWEKEZEHU MUSA FEKADA ‘ALEJHI KALE HADHA MIN ‘AMELI ESH-SHEJTANI
  28,16,KALE RABBI ‘INNI DHELEMTU NEFSI FAGFIR LI FEGAFERE LEHU ‘INNEHU HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  28,17,KALE RABBI BIMA ‘EN’AMTE ‘ALEJJE FELEN ‘EKUNE DHEHIRÆN LILMUXHRIMINE
  28,18,FE’ESBEHE FIL-MEDINETI HA’IFÆN JETEREKKABU FE’IDHAL-LEDHI ESTENSEREHU BIL-’EMSI JESTESRIHUHU KALE LEHU MUSA ‘INNEKE LEGAWIJUN MUBINUN
  28,19,FELEMMA ‘EN ‘ERADE ‘EN JEBTISHE BIEL-LEDHI HUWE ‘ADUWUN LEHUMA KALE JA MUSA ‘ETURIDU ‘EN TEKTULENI KEMA KATELTE NEFSÆN BIL-’EMSI ‘IN TURIDU ‘ILLA ‘EN TEKUNE XHEBBARÆN FIL-’ERDI WE MA TURIDU ‘EN TEKUNE MINEL-MUSLIHINE
  28,20,WE XHA’E REXHULUN MIN ‘EKSAL-MEDINETI JES’A KALE JA MUSA ‘INNEL-MELE’E JE’TEMIRUNE BIKE LIJEKTULUKE FAHRUXH ‘INNI LEKE MINE EN-NASIHINE
  28,21,FEHAREXHE MINHA HA’IFÆN JETEREKKABU KALE RABBI NEXHXHINI MINEL-KAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  28,22,WE LEMMA TEWEXHXHEHE TILKA’E MEDJENE KALE ‘ASA RABBI ‘EN JEHDIJENI SEWA’E ES-SEBIL
  28,23,WE LEMMA WEREDE MA’E MEDJENE WEXHEDE ‘ALEJHI ‘UMMETEN MINE EN-NASI JESKUNE WE WEXHEDE MIN DUNIHIMU EMRE’TEJNI TEDHUDANI KALE MA HATBUKUMA KALETA LA NESKI HETTA JUSDIRE ER-RI’A’U WE ‘EBUNA SHEJHUN KEBIRUN
  28,24,FESEKA LEHUMA THUMME TEWELLA ‘ILA EDH-DHILLI FEKALE RABBI ‘INNI LIMA ‘ENZELTE ‘ILEJJE MIN HAJRIN FEKIRUN
  28,25,FEXHA’ET/HU ‘IHDAHUMA TEMSHI ‘ALA ESTIHJA’IN KALET ‘INNE ‘EBI JED’UKE LIJEXHZIJEKE ‘EXHRE MA SEKAJTE LENA FELEMMA XHA’EHU WE KASSE ‘ALEJHIL-KASESE KALE LA TEHAF NEXHEWTE MINEL-KAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  28,26,KALET ‘IHDAHUMA JA ‘EBETI ESTE’XHIRHU ‘INNE HAJRE MENI ESTE’XHERTEL-KAWIJUL-’EMINU
  28,27,KALE ‘INNI ‘URIDU ‘EN ‘UNKIHEKE ‘IHDA EBNETEJJE HATEJNI ‘ALA ‘EN TE’XHURENI THEMANIJETE HIXHEXHIN FE’IN ‘ETMEMTE ‘ASHRÆN FEMIN ‘INDIKE WE MA ‘URIDU ‘EN ‘ESHUKKA ‘ALEJKE SETEXHIDUNI ‘IN SHA’EL-LAHU MINE ES-SALIHINE
  28,28,KALE DHALIKE BEJNI WE BEJNEKE ‘EJJEMAL-’EXHELEJNI KADEJTU FELA ‘UDWANE ‘ALEJJE WEL-LAHU ‘ALA MA NEKULU WE KILUN